ActDepartment of Citizenship and Immigration Act
Immigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectSaskatchewan Contribution Agreement for the Enhanced Language Training Initiative
PrecisOrder approving that the Minister enter into a contribution AGREEMENT with the Government of Saskatchewan, for the purpose of facilitating the implementation of the ENHANCED LANGUAGE TRAINING INITIATIVE for immigrants and refugees, for a term ending on March 31, 2013.
